# Ignore everything under static/targets/ (user uploads) EXCEPT the bundled
# seed image. nasp_40cm.jpg is the default target seeded for every new user
# AND the placeholder under every tournament face — it must ship so a fresh
# clone works out of the box. Note: must ignore the *contents* (targets/*),
# not the directory itself, or git can't re-include a file inside it.
static/targets/*
!static/targets/nasp_40cm.jpg
wsgi_snippet.py
inject_gtag.py
venv/

